<item>
            <title>[CXF-8080] MP Rest Client CompletionStages from async methods are never completed</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-8080</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/manish2aug&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;Manish Kumar&lt;/a&gt; first reported this issue in a [Twitter post|&lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/manish2aug/status/1155558627593379842&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://twitter.com/manish2aug/status/1155558627593379842&lt;/a&gt;]&#160;and then opened issue &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/eclipse/microprofile-rest-client/issues/208&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;208&lt;/a&gt;&#160;on the MP Rest Client spec page.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;He provided an example that shows that the CompletionStage never completes, leaving his test case hung. &#160;See the example here:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://gist.github.com/manish2aug/b4133b9fbedc2175e15b303a0682b552&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://gist.github.com/manish2aug/b4133b9fbedc2175e15b303a0682b552&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It should be possible to fix this with a change to the MPRestClientCallback.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
